Giant frogs are monsters found in the Lumbridge Swamp, the Lumbridge Swamp Caves and Dorgesh-Kaan South Dungeon. The level 99 variants are the toughest monster in the dungeon. They are found to the south of the cave system, just outside the entrance to Juna's Chasm of Tears.

Their low Defence, high number of hitpoints, and big bones they drop make them a useful monster for training combat skills. Their frequent drops of nature runes and giant frog legs, which can be sold to Hudo in the Tree Gnome Stronghold for 1,000 coins a piece, when combined to their closeness to the Lumbridge Castle and Culinaromancer's Chest banks, can also make training fairly profitable.
